1. *Zatvorena* vrata su nam zaštitila od zimskog vremena. (The closed door protected us from the winter weather.)
2. Često zaboravljamo da zaključamo *zatvorene* prozore. (We often forget to lock the closed windows.)
3. *Zatvaranje* ulaza je obavezno tokom noći. (Closing the entrance is mandatory during the night.)
4. Moramo da se pridržavamo *zatvorenih* pravila. (We must abide by the closed rules.)
5. Tvoja *zatvorena* priroda čini te zanimljivijim. (Your closed nature makes you more interesting.)